Fig. 23. Segmentally dilated apoeccrine secretory portion. Only a short segment was removed from the large apoeccrine secretory coil for ultrastructural study. For detailed ultrastructure of cross-sections 1 and 4, see reference 133. A, Isolated segment photographed before embedding. B, Embedded tissue, 1 ~m thick, cut along the line shown in A.
